e":"Scenario: Gingivitis and periodontitis"},{"id":"46382643-0f59-56b1-907b-5e667b684585","slug":"acute-necrotizing-ulcerative-gingivitis","fullItemName":"Scenario: Acute necrotizing ulcerative gingivitis"}]},{"id":"21f82196-e0cc-579f-a4aa-260db78f847d","fullItemName":"Prescribing information","slug":"prescribing-information","subChapters":[{"id":"e6372bc4-e135-58b6-8df8-0d3f12a0a2ea","slug":"amoxicillin","fullItemName":"Amoxicillin"},{"id":"84cd4551-a452-5789-8752-e0c6eb4bc87f","slug":"chlorhexidine","fullItemName":"Chlorhexidine"},{"id":"b9acc98e-caa3-5de2-8c27-0021d062e7c6","slug":"metronidazole","fullItemName":"Metronidazole"}]},{"id":"fa338d9c-c007-5424-a185-d45d3cc97aaa","fullItemName":"Supporting evidence","slug":"supporting-evidence","subChapters":[]},{"id":"5d32b973-0a04-5d8c-b893-01ef9ed83901","fullItemName":"How this topic was developed","slug":"how-this-topic-was-developed","subChapters":[{"id":"90a0f50a-373e-5e79-b347-ef01e0b5414b","slug":"search-strategy","fullItemName":"Search strategy"},{"id":"5677a363-6aaa-51f8-8718-070e5c7f6636","slug":"stakeholder-engagement","fullItemName":"Stakeholder engagement"},{"id":"47be6692-bf87-5832-8dfe-c5be55c71004","slug":"evidence-exclusion-criteria","fullItemName":"Evidence exclusion criteria"},{"id":"ab73eb28-31fa-545f-939a-53d4e82c18b0","slug":"organizational-behavioural-financial-barriers","fullItemName":"Organizational, behavioural and financial barriers"},{"id":"91e54862-93aa-5c58-820e-b47769d73d34","slug":"declarations-of-interest","fullItemName":"Declarations of interest"}]},{"id":"b8f01d98-81c5-5a1a-9159-64f8b79ff85c","fullItemName":"References","slug":"references","subChapters":[]}]},"parentChapter":{"id":"07bf77ad-d5e5-5c15-8d6e-ed41f1db4df3","slug":"diagnosis","fullItemName":"Diagnosis"},"subChapters":[{"id":"fed2f2aa-09d6-5c9e-ad45-0caa7bdc16d3","slug":"basis-for-recommendation-846","fullItemName":"Basis for recommendation","depth":3,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field e19d5d0d-30fc-4c84-afcc-57d35199eb1c --><h3>Basis for recommendation</h3><!-- end field e19d5d0d-30fc-4c84-afcc-57d35199eb1c -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item 846b5cf1-c150-4977-897f-b173b9a150e9 --><!-- begin field bb320db2-a1df-44c1-8989-fe55eb28b101 --><p>Information on the differential diagnosis of gingivitis and periodontitis is based on a guideline from the Scottish Dental Clinical Effectiveness Programme [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/gingivitis-periodontitis/references/\">Scottish Dental Clinical Effectiveness Programme, 2014</a>],<strong> </strong>expert opinion from review articles [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/gingivitis-periodontitis/references/\">Scully and Porter, 1997</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/gingivitis-periodontitis/references/\">Meraw and Sheridan, 1998</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/gingivitis-periodontitis/references/\">Coventry et al, 2000</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/gingivitis-periodontitis/references/\">Atout and Todescan, 2013</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/gingivitis-periodontitis/references/\">BMJ Best Practice, 2016</a>], and a textbook [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/gingivitis-periodontitis/references/\">Lehner and Challacombe, 2010</a>]. </p><!-- end field bb320db2-a1df-44c1-8989-fe55eb28b101 --><!-- end item 846b5cf1-c150-4977-897f-b173b9a150e9 -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}